comments.body:
It's less a Golang issue and more of a CNI issue, nearest I can tell.

We use https://github.com/containernetworking/cni to configure the system firewall and forward network traffic (and ports on the host) to containers. However, CNI does not at present support SCTP, to the best of my knowledge, so we can't tell it to poke holes in the firewall for SCTP traffic to the container.

@dcbw would know more here (and about potential plans for adding support)
